{"TopicId":141184,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Mod to quit the game faster.","CreatedByName":"SuperFastJellyfish","CreatedById":57985,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T10:39:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SuperFastJellyfish","CreatedById":57985,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T10:39:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI love this game.\u00A0 Have loved it for years. I don\u0027t leave the \u0027Science Labs\u0027 on these forums too often, but has someone made a mod to immediately quit the game?\u00A0 As much as I love pressing Esc (load)-\u0026gt; \u0027Back to Main Menu\u0027(load) -\u0026gt; Back(load) -\u0026gt; Quit(load) -\u0026gt; Quit(load), I\u0027d much rather have more of a tight, manual control over my computer and be able to exit the application immediately without the seemingly unnecessary loading phases.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know I can just right click the application on the taskbar and close the program, but that feels \u0027unnatural\u0027.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u00A0 Thanks for your input, in advance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-04T10:40:47Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2016 10:40  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by SuperFastJellyfish\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T10:43:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85834-11x105-malahs-quick-mods-updated-quickstart-beta-20160525/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-04T10:44:12Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2016 10:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Speadge\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuperFastJellyfish","CreatedById":57985,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T10:47:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome, thanks for the link.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T10:48:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222615890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465037260\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257985\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SuperFastJellyfish\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, SuperFastJellyfish said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome, thanks for the link.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwelcome\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cantab","CreatedById":104935,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T11:05:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF4 works too. I think it was confirmed that provided you don\u0027t do it while the game is saving, there\u0027s no problem with using it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drew Kerman","CreatedById":103177,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T17:11:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222615907\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465038307\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104935\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cantab\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, cantab said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF4 works too. I think it was confirmed that provided you don\u0027t do it while the game is saving, there\u0027s no problem with using it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nseconded. I do it all. the. time. From everywhere in the game. Never a single issue I could ever trace back to doing this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-05T10:33:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222615907\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465038307\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104935\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cantab\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, cantab said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF4 works too. I think it was confirmed that provided you don\u0027t do it while the game is saving, there\u0027s no problem with using it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222616244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465060307\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103177\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gaiiden\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Gaiiden said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nseconded. I do it all. the. time. From everywhere in the game. Never a single issue I could ever trace back to doing this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThirded! I hardly ever quit by going back to the main menu. From in flight I tend to go back to the space center view and then alt-f4 (as that ensures a save), but everywhere else I just hit alt-f4.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MircoMars","CreatedById":61811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-05T12:18:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyup,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nF5 \u0026amp;\u00A0Alt-F4 : hello desktop\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif a\u00A0game really\u00A0got stuck\u00A0the fasted way is ctrl-shift-esc to open taskmgr and then end process\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nright now I need something to make the game quit slower because of massive\u00A0CTD issues... \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/140001-bust-11x-crashes-your-help-requested\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ebut this is another topic\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mjarf","CreatedById":16666,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-05T12:21:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI usually run KSP windowed, so most of the time I just click on the \u0022X\u0022 in the top right corner. Yes, I\u00A0admit that I have crashed ships because I was browsing Facebook during descent.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Reaper_Works","CreatedById":160425,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-06T23:47:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalt-f4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}